                <p> Let's say <%=@wolf.user.name%> put a reward of $ 500. If you help to send the request to Fasil, and Fasil twitted it to his friend Roland and luckily Roland find it!  <%=@wolf.user.name%> will pay Roland $ 500, Fasil $250 and you $125. </p></br>

                <p> So start ask people to join your search network through this link <code><%=@url %></code>. <br><br>

                <p> Asking <strong>personally</strong> and <strong>nicely</strong> for help is always more effective than broadcast and spam. </p><br>


                <p class="lead">Mobilize through poster</p>

                <p>Print out this page, the QR code is the link to your search network.</p><br>

                <!-- this section should be hidden for owner of the wolf -->
                <% unless @wolf.user == current_user %>
                
	                <div class="titlearea">
	                    <h2>Submit a tip</h2>
	                </div>
	                
		    	    <%= render 'shared/shoot', :smoke => @smoke %>
	    	    
	    	    <% end %>



                <div class="poster">

                <i class="press icon-bullhorn icon-2x pull-left"></i>
                <p class="lead">“Life is like riding a bicycle. To keep your balance, you must keep moving.” </p>



                </div>


              </div>




    </div>
